```dart
Future<Database> initDatabase() async {
  return await openDatabase(
    join(await getDatabasesPath(), 'notes.db'),
    onCreate: (db, version) {
      return db.execute(
        'CREATE TABLE notes(id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, titre TEXT, contenu TEXT, dateCreation TEXT)',
      );
    },
    version: 1,
  );
}
```

```dart
Future<int> insertNote(Note note) async {
  Database db = await initDatabase();
  return await db.insert('notes', note.toMap());
}
```

```dart
Future<List<Note>> getAllNotes() async {
  Database db = await initDatabase();
  final List<Map<String, dynamic>> maps = await db.query(
    'notes',
    orderBy: 'dateCreation DESC',
  );
  return List.generate(maps.length, (i) => Note.fromMap(maps[i]));
}
```

```dart
Future<void> deleteNote(BuildContext context, int id) async {
  bool? confirm = await showDialog<bool>(
    context: context,
    builder: (ctx) => AlertDialog(
      title: Text('Supprimer'),
      content: Text('Voulez-vous vraiment supprimer cette note ?'),
      actions: [
        TextButton(onPressed: () => Navigator.pop(ctx, false), child: Text('Non')),
        TextButton(onPressed: () => Navigator.pop(ctx, true), child: Text('Oui')),
      ],
    ),
  );
  if (confirm == true) {
    Database db = await initDatabase();
    await db.delete('notes', where: 'id = ?', whereArgs: [id]);
    _loadNotes(); // Recharge la liste
  }
}
```

Dans la méthode `onUpgrade` de `openDatabase`, on vérifie l'ancienne version. Si `oldVersion < 2`, on exécute `ALTER TABLE notes ADD COLUMN estArchive INTEGER DEFAULT 0`. SQLite ne supporte pas le type booléen, on utilise 0 (false) ou 1 (true).

```dart
onUpgrade: (db, oldVersion, newVersion) async {
  if (oldVersion < 2) {
    await db.execute('ALTER TABLE notes ADD COLUMN estArchive INTEGER DEFAULT 0');
  }
}
```
On incrémente `version: 2` dans `openDatabase`.
